(a) Definition of animal improvement:
It refers to means/techiques of developing/breeding/producing animals of better traits/characters over the existing ones /parents
OR It is a means/technique of introduction/selection/breeding of animals with better/outstanding traits/character/genes/allele over the existing ones (b) Explanation of the terms;
Cross breeding;
It is the mating of proven quality animals from different breeds but the same species e.g. Muturu  x White Fulani. It leads to production of heterosis/hybrid vigour
Out breeding;
It is the mating of unrelated animals of the same breed It recovers certain traits that may have been lost due to other breeding methods. New traits are introduced in the offspring/young ones
